@baseUrl = https://y36enrj145.execute-api.ap-southeast-2.amazonaws.com/v1
@tenantCode = demo-school
@tenantId = ten_demo
@courseId = crs_demo_001
@idempotencyKey = 3c579f90-4962-4a49-9ced-e6a37f63500a

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Org auth sanity (mock mode headers)
GET {{baseUrl}}/org/me
x-user-id: user_1
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}
x-role: org_admin

### Public list
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/{{tenantCode}}/courses

### Public detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/{{tenantCode}}/courses/{{courseId}}

### Public enrollment submit (idempotent)
POST {{baseUrl}}/public/{{tenantCode}}/courses/{{courseId}}/enrollments
content-type: application/json
idempotency-key: {{idempotencyKey}}

{
  "formVersion": 1,
  "answers": {
    "first_name": "Alice",
    "email": "alice@example.com",
    "consent_terms": true
  },
  "meta": {
    "locale": "en-NZ",
    "timezone": "Pacific/Auckland"
  }
}
